QuestData.Title: Big Trouble in Moonbrook
QuestData.Description: I'll be filling out my report and heading back to Stormwind shortly. SI: 7 must be informed of the happenings in Westfall. I would recommend you do the same and report back to Gryan.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report your findings to Marshal Gryan Stoutmantle at Sentinel Hill in Westfall.
QuestData.RewardText: Who IS this Shadowy Figure? We have to get to Moonbrook.
